Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:04.24,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仰望天空 广阔梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:08.18,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}打开未来的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:15.18,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:25.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明朗的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.95,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}打开窗便有阳光洒下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}微风拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:36.43,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}拭去昨日的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.92,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}寂寞之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}总是寻找着看不见的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.07,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不知它近在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:52.32,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}依然不断追求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.70,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}（you are the shining star）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:57.21,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}仰望天空 广阔梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:01:01.15,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}打开未来的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:07.78,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}此刻依然无限光芒照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.29,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}星空闪烁的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:15.32,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}不计其数的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:21.65,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}如今依然等待着你去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:26.36,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}所以迈步前进吧
