Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.97,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:31.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.65,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:48.28,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:52.46,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.28,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:23:00.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:03.08,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:07.88,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:11.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:18.24,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:20.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:21.88,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:26.07,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:30.69,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.86,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.62,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:41.99,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.80,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:46.19,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:49.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:54.31,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
