Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦助的小鸟不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离巢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经长成大鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a safe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君真坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦率？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真庆幸初次登台的对手是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要练习一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想用一下厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班的小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说今早也在禁断的行星赏鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁断的行星？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是男厕所啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男厕所赏鸟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人小弟在学艺会上要亲亲的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和子妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君太受欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野只是像对乌鸦和副部长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我取乐而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受欢迎啊 拓人小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不懂女人心啊 拓人小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 和子妹妹那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤少爷可怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有两个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能当我画画的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你绝对应该当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是命运了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为此而生的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第一队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「国王」的代表之座还为你空着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们随时准备迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是准备在这里使用王之柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神赐予的才能 必然是有意义的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有战士之印也就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有强大的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说野心也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士的驭星者没有人能赢得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你胸前刻下的并非战士之印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是王之印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个银河美少年即将被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒没打算取他性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也视他为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤野？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你借点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…听阿姨说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和平时一样说些开心的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是水野喜欢的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦助的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鸦助还喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是那个副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比副部长还喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君的确是很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道鞠野也对拓人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都是水野的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我就不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代的驭星者总算齐聚一堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果人面狮一次都没来过这间房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她使用Ayingott之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她说没找到是说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长说谎的女孩子 真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动之后还被叫出来习武
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是太过分了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚气势不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能挤下三个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子选个喜欢的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下次练习是打赌赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打赌赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟和子的婚约就一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你可以进她的伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该从哪儿吐槽好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玩笑 我可当真了哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈你个头啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君对和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的话是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假的话 至少告诉我一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你巫女的身份被谁发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是感觉不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能瞒多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言说通 就会成为真实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 谎言编造的世界是虚幻的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22\b0\fsp0\fs18}（注：参见本片第10话）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实就是不会消逝的虚幻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吧 水野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吧 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0\fad(0,500)}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如 见见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分开再分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是面对面说清楚比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是不是真的抛弃了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能继续前行不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也想见见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说「其实」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么鞠野会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出姐姐的架子 说些自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人 为什么现在又回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出姐姐的架子 说些自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为她回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚捞的蝾螺 要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的我有些古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想到她也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她在岛上的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等那个人离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另附
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来是第一次去本土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么点小激动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚捞的蝾螺 要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是预知梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土购物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能载我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆搭讪 最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 第一次去本土？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全驾驶 加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 暖暖手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再握一次我的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子现在 真的在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上起 岛上的空气就在躁动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试离开岛上了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…和子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是净身的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女的职责？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:20:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说今晨开始结界躁动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是些粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是日死之巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没尝试过离开岛上是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子是巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 也离不开岛上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有 巫女的职责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上的四方巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守口如瓶 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来我们这儿商量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:46.24,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢这翠色的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.06,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}风又带来夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}千回辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:59.09,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}万回闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:04.20,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光就这样诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开岛上的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日死之巫女同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有我必须做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你是日死之巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人之印
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊吧 驯化！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------


